Start up procedure:
-Plug in the power supply and screen (should be combined onto one extension cord that can be plugged in)
-The raspberry pi computer will automatically start up
-Ensure the bluetooth controller is charged and turn it on.
-Double click start_programv2.sh on the desktop and a dialog box will pop up, click execute and this should start the powerpoint
-Take the turn of the knob in order to switch through the slides

Power down procedure:
-Press the x in the upper right corner
-Click the raspberry in the lower left corner and press shutdown, then shutdown on the dialog box
-After 30 seconds, unplug the screen and control box. If you do not do this, you will need to power cycle before next startup. 
